high_descs: Look at the ground, then turn left and walk forward, then turn to your right and  go forward to where the desk is.
Grab the alarm clock in the very back.
Do a 180 degree turn and walk forward halfway between the bed and desk, then turn left walk forward to the bookcase and turn left again, walk to the desk with the Cd,
Place the alarm clock to the left of the Cd.
